<br>
It's my understanding, that just getting to PoM is close to impossible.  There is a corridor with level 70 dragon mobs that are KoS to everything regardless of faction. So, IF you make it through there, you get to PoM to fight mobs that drop nothing and have random HP. <br>
<br>
The only successful strategy of making it to PoM that I have heard of, is using a rez stick.  Basically, the raid group dies on the way up, and a rogue, with the right faction (not sure what that faction is) can invis and drag bodies through that corridor (not sure how this works with the new dragging rules with bad faction).  Once there, the rogue uses the rez stick to rez the cleric who then rezzes everyone else.  <br>
<br>
Now, I am not sure about anyone else, but if I even suggested to my guild that I wanted to try this, I would probably get laughed at, hehe.  Has anyone heard of any other good strategy plans for getting to PoM or any alternatives for completing this quest? Thanks =)<br>
